Review Text: Ordered signature platters chicken is so soft and delicious.. Had a decent lunch with hot delivery Worth taking for the money you spent...!!
I'm a frequent customer of this food. Based on reviews i personally went to the place which is near by me. Their hygiene conditions are pretty good and food is hot and tasty.

When u are a vegetarian be aware they will send u non veg stuff. Plus zomato , u will remember the videos that were shared in social media. Their staff is hungary so will have a bite on way. Burger is stone cold, probably made in morning for evening deliveries. Best part is zomato delivery boy as per profile can speak hindi and english but when u tell issue has no clue what u talking about.
Taste nice and costumer friendly. They also give discount. Enough good and healthy evening snacks. If u want spicy snacks go for it. Happy eve.
Nice place to have a quality and tasty food with different recipes and multiple special sauces with low price point. Complement to taste new product for every order.

Ordered their signature chicken burger. The meat patty tasted like boiled & minced soyabean. I took small bites of meat 2-3 times to verify if, by mistake, they delivered wrong item. Finally had to throw the minced stuff away.
There is nothing nice about the food unfortunately.

I ordered their TBS Signature Chicken Burger along with crispy wings + drum and I was very much underwhelmed with the burger. 
They advertise the burger being served with fries, lettuce, crispy onions, tomato and signature sauce but what I got was some soggy onions with a defrosted patty in an over toasted crispy bun. Everything else was missing, even the add on cheese for which I paid extra.
The coating on wings was good but then there was minimal to no meat inside.
Their signature spicy sauce was okish, I have had better.
